\id JUD Mike Anderson; (Sudest or Tagula); PNG; March, 1998; Solomon Joshua
\h Jiud
\toc1 Letake Iyake Jiud Le Rorori
\toc2 Jiud
\toc3 Jiud
\mt2 Letake Iyake
\mt1 Jiud
\mt2 Le Rorori
\imt1 Utu iviva
\ip Letake iyake ghararorori Jiud o raŇča Judas. Idae mbe reghaeŇčge ko ghaunouno theghewo. Judas th…® ghanagha Buk Boboma e t…®ne, ko raghareghare lemoyo th…®Ňča letake iyake ghararorori iye Judas Jisas ghaghae regha (Matiu 13:55). Na iye tembe Jemes, iye Jerusalem ekelesiya gharandeviva ghaghae (r…®ghe 1).
\ip Jiud va i roriya letake iyake na i variye weŇčgiya ekelesiya vavana, kaiwae ravavaghare kwan…®kwan vavana kaero ina e t…®nenji. Iya kaiwae Jiud iŇča nuwaiya i vavur…®ghegheŇčgi na th…® rogaith…® loŇčweghath…® e gharogaith…® e t…®ne na thavala th…® wogaith…® weya vavaghare thovuye th…® utu varumwara nuwanji. ‚ÄúLoŇčweghath…®ko iyako Loi va i wogiya weŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…®, na ma val…®kaiwae ra v…®v…® na ma reghaova‚ÄĚ (r…®ghe 3).
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ghino Jiud, Jisas Krais le rakakaiwo na Jemes ghaghae, ya roriya letake iyake na ya variye e ghemi thavala Loi kaerova i kula e ghemi. Ghemi Loi Ramanda i gharethovuŇčga na Jisas Krais i njimbukikiŇčga:
\p 
\v 2 Ya naŇčgo Loi iye mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye i gharev…®r…®ŇčaŇčga, le gharemal…®l…® i riyevanjara gharemi, na huya yaku ele gharethovu riyeriyevanjaraniye t…®ne.
\s1 Ravavaghare kwan…®kwan lenji thar…® vuyowae weŇčgi utuniye
\p 
\v 3 Wouna na val…®ghareghareŇčgu, va nuwaŇčguiya moli ya roriya lemi leta na ya utuŇča iya vamoruke iya taulagh…®ke ra vaidi utuniye, ko e mbaŇčake iyake nuwaŇčguiya moli ya utuŇča bigi regha utuniye. NuwaŇčguiya ya utu vavur…®gheghe e ghemi na loŇčweghath…® ghagaith…® hu gaith…®we na hu vikikighath…®gha budakaiya ghinda raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® ra ndeghath…®we. LoŇčweghath…®ko iyako Loi va i wogiya weŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…®, na ma val…®kaiwae ra v…®v…® na ma reghaova.
\v 4 Kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® vavana, thiye ma th…® yavwatatawana Loi, kaero th…® ru thuwele e lemi wabwina t…®ne. Thiye th…® v…®v…® Loi le mwaewo bwagabwaga utuniye gharerenuwaŇča na th…® munjeva lenji var…®voru, ko amba th…® vakavakatha yathima thanavuniye raraithar…®. Ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako Jisas Krais, iye mbe ghambereghaeŇčge GiyanduŇčenduŇče na ghanda Giya, th…® botewoyathu. MbaŇča va i vivako Buk Boboma kaerova i woraŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Ňčgoranjiyako ne th…® vaidiya vuyowo lagh…®ye.
\p 
\v 5 Kaero hu ghareghare Giya Loi va i vaŇčgu raŇčgiyaŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye vuyowo e t…®ne Ijipt, na muyai tembe i mukuwoŇčgiva thavala mava th…® loŇčweghath…®, ko iyemaeŇčge nuwaŇčguiya tembe ya ravair…®veŇčgava na hu rerenuwaŇča kaiwae.
\v 6 Hu renuwaŇčakikiŇčgiya nyao thovuthovuye, iya thiye va th…® botewoyathu ghamba yakuko Loi va i woveŇčgiko, na th…® roiteta lenji ghamba yakuko. Loi kaero va i yaŇčgar…®Ňčgi e sen memeghabananiye na i vaŇčguraweŇčgi e momouwo t…®ne, th…® roroghagha na ghambaŇča lagh…®ye na i woraweya ghanjimbaro.
\v 7 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Sodoma na Gomora na ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji, th…® vakavakatha thegha na gamaina thanavuniye na th…® vatomweŇčgi yathima e thanavuniye mbe vavanaŇčgiva Ňčgoreiya nyaoma lenji vakatha. Ghanjithanavuma modae th…® nda e nd…®ghe, na thiye Ňčgoranjiya ghamba thuwathuwa Loi nevole i lith…® weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e nd…®ghe memeghabananiye t…®ne.
\p 
\v 8 Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake iyava th…® ru thuwelema e lemi wabwina t…®ne, thanavuko iya reghako tembe th…® vakavakathava. Th…® goru weya lenji gheneloloko na th…® vakowana riwanji na th…® vamb…®gh…®ya e yathima thanavuniye. Th…® botewoyathu Loi le mbaro, na th…® utuvathar…® weŇčgiya buruburu vur…®vur…®ghegheniye.
\v 9 Nyao thovuye giyaninji regha idae Maikol, weiye Seitan th…® wogaith…®, th…® rorovur…®gheghe Mosese riwae kaiwae na thela i wo. E mbaŇčako iyako Maikol mava nuwaiya i utuvathar…® weya Seitan, vambema iŇča eŇčge, ‚ÄúGiya i lith…® e ghen!‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Ravavaghare kwan…®kwan…®ke thiyake ma th…® ghareghareya bigibigike thiyake ghanjirumwaru, mbema th…® utuvathar…® eŇčge weŇčgi. Th…® ghareghareya bigibigi vavana, ko lenji renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiya thetheghan mbwanjam, ghareghareko iyako i vakowana yawalinji.
\p 
\v 11 Aleu, ghanjithar…® lagh…®ya iyako! Kaero th…® ghambugha thanavuko iya Kein va i reŇčakowe. Th…® numo mani na kaero th…® vatomweŇčgi Baalam le thar…® e t…®ne. Thiye th…® gaith…® weya Loi Ňčgoreiya Kora\f + \fr 1:11 \ft Kora i vaŇčguvathavatha ghar…®ghar…® na th…® th…®gh…®ya wanaŇčgiya Mosese na Eron. Loi i gharegaith…® lagh…®yewe na i vakatha thelau na i mwanaviya na i kovululuŇčgiya Kora na gharaghambu.\f* i botewoyathu Mosese le mbaro na i gaith…®wana, na Loi ne i mukuwoŇčgi Ňčgoreiya va i mukuwaŇčgiya Kora na le wabwi.
\p 
\v 12 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake e umbalinjiko mbe thar…® eŇčge, na e lenji vakathako mbe thiye eŇčge vara kaiwanji na i monjimonjina. Th…® vakowana lemi ekelesiyana ghan…®ŇčganiyeŇčgi mbaŇča hu ghan…®Ňčga weimiyaŇčgi. Th…® wovoreŇča ghanjimberegha na tembe thiye th…® njimbukikiŇčgi. Thiye Ňčgoranjiya Ňčgal…®l…® ndewendewe i uvevewoŇčgi na ma e uyeniye, na tembe Ňčgoranjiva umbwa ghanjimbaŇča rau na ma e uneunenji. Kaero th…® mare, iya kaiwae th…® ther…®yathuŇčgi na th…® mare moli.
\v 13 Thiye Ňčgoranjiya Ňčgonu lagh…®lagh…®ye e njigh…®ko th…® bebe na lenji vakathako monjinaniye Ňčgoreiya bagoduko njoŇčgonjoŇčgowae. Thiye Ňčgoranjiya gh…®tara th…® vathavwiya lenji ghamba reŇča na th…® ghawe moli. Loi kaerova i vivatharaweya ghambanji, momouwo lagh…®ye moli inawe na ne veth…® roghabanawe moli.
\p 
\v 14 Inok iye Adam rumbuye tha theghepir…®ninji va le dagerawe ghar…®ghar…® Ňčgoranjiyako kaiwanji, iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe! Giya i menamenako weiyaŇčgiya le Nyao Thovuye lemoyo lemoyo moli,
\v 15 ne th…® rakamena th…® vakot…®Ňčgiya thar…® gharavakathaŇčgiko wolagh…®ye, thavala ma th…® yavwatatawana Loi na i wogiya ghanjivuyowo. Kaiwae ma weinji lenji yavwatata weya Loi e lenji vakathako wolagh…®ye e t…®ne na th…® utuutuvathar…®we.‚ÄĚ
\v 16 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake ghanjiune mbe th…® romban eŇčge e ghaenji na th…® vewonjowonjoweŇčgi. Tembe th…® ghambugha ghanjimberegha lenji renuwaŇča raraithar…®. Tembe ghanjimberegha th…® wovoreŇčaŇčgi na lenji utuko i wo ghanjiune nuwanji th…® vaŇčguŇčgi na th…® reŇča e lenji renuwaŇčako.
\s1 Utu vavur…®gheghe vavana
\p 
\v 17 Ko lo bodaboda na val…®ghareghareŇčgu, hu renuwaŇčakikiya budakai ghanda Giya Jisas Krais ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® va lenji utuma weŇčga.
\v 18 Va th…® utu e ghemi na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne ele ghambako ghar…®ghar…® vavana ne th…® yomara na th…® vav…®ra lemi loŇčweghath…®na weya Loi. Thiye ma th…® yavwatatawana Loi na tembe ghanjimberegha th…® ghambugha lenji renuwaŇča raraithar…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 19 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake th…® vakatha wabwi na wabwi e lemi ekelesiya na t…®ne, na th…® mbela yambaneke renuwaŇčaniye. Nyao Boboma ma ina weŇčgi.
\p 
\v 20 Ko ghemi, lo bodaboda val…®ghareghareŇčgu, lemi loŇčweghath…®na thovuyena moli iya i menana weya Loi; iye ghamimbagh…®mbagh…®, na yawalimina hu vatad vavur…®gheghe e mbagh…®mbagh…®ko iyako, na hu naŇčgonaŇčgo Nyao Boboma ele vur…®gheghe t…®ne.
\v 21 Loi i gharethovu kaiwami, na hu njimbukikiya ghamithanavuna na hu yaku ele gharethovu t…®ne. Na hu roroghagha ghanda Giya Jisas Krais weiye le gharev…®r…® i giya yawal…® memeghabananiye weŇčga.
\v 22 Ghamune vavana th…® numoghegheiwo na lenji loŇčweghath…® i njavovo, mbe gharemi weŇčgi na hu thalavuŇčgi.
\v 23 Na vavana Ňčgoranjiya inanji e nd…®ghe une, hu vur…®gheghe hu vaŇčgu raŇčgiyaŇčgi e thar…®ko t…®ne. Vavana riwanjiko yawaliye i yalaweghath…®Ňčgi, mbe gharemi weŇčgi, ko iyemaeŇčge mbe weimi lemi mararu na hu njimbukikiŇčga mbala thava lenji thar…®ma thanavuniye i lawa e ghemi na i vamb…®gh…®yaŇčga. Hu njimbukiki wagiyaweŇčga na hu botewoyathu riwanjina thanavuniye raraithar…®, ne iwaeŇčge i vamb…®gh…®yaŇčga.
\s1 Loi ghatarawa
\p 
\v 24 Loi iye val…®kaiwae ne i njimbukikiŇčga na mane hu dobu, na val…®kaiwae ne i vaŇčguŇčga na i vaŇčguraweŇčga amalagh…®niye Ravwenyevwenye e marae, na mane e lemi thar…® na warari i riyevanjaraŇčga.
\v 25 Iye mbe ghambereghaeŇčge Loi emunjoru na iye ghanda Ravamoru, iya kaiwae Jisas Krais ghanda Giya e idae ra tarawe na raŇča iye Ravwenyevwenye, Ramevoro, Ravur…®gheghe na Rambarombaro Moli, iye Ňčgoreiya mbaŇča va i vivako, mbaŇčake noroke, na mbaŇčake i menamenake ma ele ghambako. Mbwana. Ňägoreiye. 
